snippet.title: Trago ~ SpaceGiraff3
snippet.description:
Trago is a multi-choice adventure game that brings feelings of night pubs in Brazil. 

The game tells the story of Juca, a regular guy that goes everyday at the same hour to this low budget bar called Trago. It's a game about tragedy. The characters: Juca, Joana and Carlos guide you throught a mystery story about trust, friendship and death.
